data.description: GREAT INCOME POTENTIAL OR MULTI-FAMILY LIVING! 3 HOMES ON OVER 5 ACRES! Looking for your own country paradise? Well, you have found it! This amazing 5.5-acre country property offers endless opportunities and a prime location! The adorable main house boasts approximately 1,350 sq ft. and serves as the central hub of the property. Features include a cozy kitchen, 3 bedrooms, one bathroom, living room, family room, dining room, laundry room and basement. Adjacent to the main home is a charming cottage, offering a kitchen, small dining area, living room, a bedroom and 3/4 bathroom. The cottage's compact size ensures easy maintenance and a cozy atmosphere, making it an ideal option for those desiring a simpler lifestyle.  The  third dwelling is a spacious 3-bedroom, 2 bath manufactured home on a permanent foundation.  Additionally, a cute shed with front porch has been converted into a bunkhouse. This additional space can be utilized as a guest house or a recreational area for children and teenagers, offering a unique and fun living experience, providing extra sleeping quarters and a place for entertainment or relaxation.  Surrounded by 5.4 acres of picturesque countryside, this property offers ample outdoor space for various activities and hobbies. The expansive land can be utilized for gardening, outdoor gatherings, livestock or agriculture. The serene and peaceful environment provides a perfect backdrop for enjoying nature and creating lasting memories with loved ones. This property truly has so much to offer and is definitely a MUST SEE! Don't wait! Call today for your private showing and don't forget to check out the 3-D virtual tours!
